==Demographics==
As of the 2020 United States census, there were 485,773 people residing in the town. The population density was . The racial makeup of the town was 83.0% White (including 72.0% Non-Hispanic Whites), 6.1% Black or African American, 0.1% Native American, 4.7% Asian, 0.1% Pacific Islander, and 3.8% from two or more races. Hispanic or Latino people of any race were 15.6% of the population.

